42.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Jaime-Cersei-Lannister-game-of-thrones-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Jaime-Cersei-Lannister-game-of-thrones-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>据粉丝称， <a href="https://www.nme.com/series/game-of-thrones"><em>《权力的游戏》</em></a>中的乔佛里·拜拉席恩是有史以来最令人讨厌的电视角色。</p><p>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/hbo">HBO</a>剧集中由杰克·格里森 (Jack Gleeson) 饰演的这个角色在<a href="https://www.ranker.com/list/most-hated-tv-characters/matthewcoleweiss" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Ranker</em></a>评选的最不受欢迎的电视角色中名列前茅。截至撰写本文时（11 月 28 日），该名单已累计获得超过 27.34 万张选票。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/tv-reviews/house-of-the-dragon-review-game-of-thrones-3293830">《龙之屋》评论：《权力的游戏》传奇继续保持风格</a></strong></li></ul><p>虽然排名确实有所波动，但正如<a href="https://twitter.com/LordSnow/status/1728792033639158218" target="_blank" rel="noopener">最近在社交媒体上疯传的一份名单</a>所示，拉姆齐·博尔顿（伊万·瑞恩饰）目前排名第二，其次是<em>《钢之炼金术师》的</em>修·塔克和<a href="https://www.nme.com/series/the-walking-dead"><em>《行尸走肉</em></a>》的总督（大卫·莫里西饰）。 </p><figure id="attachment_3550074" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3550074" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3550074" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Joffrey-Game-Of-Thrones-main.jpg" alt="权力的游戏中的杰克·格里森" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Joffrey-Game-Of-Thrones-main.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Joffrey-Game-Of-Thrones-main-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Joffrey-Game-Of-Thrones-main-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Joffrey-Game-Of-Thrones-main-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Joffrey-Game-Of-Thrones-main-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Joffrey-